    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在新的苏联朋克动作射击游戏中对抗<strong>苏联机器人</strong>。见证<strong>旧世界</strong>的废墟和新的<strong>反乌托邦现实</strong>的恐怖。使用您的控制论力量和无限的愤怒来摧毁<strong>苏联</strong>一次并<strong>彻底</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/5cafbbab6819761405c1a9c89bbc32b7.avif?t=1765038303\" width=616 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/ef42ff4b5c1a3b833a83bc69facd63c1.poster.avif?t=1765038303\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/ef42ff4b5c1a3b833a83bc69facd63c1.webm?t=1765038303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/ef42ff4b5c1a3b833a83bc69facd63c1.mp4?t=1765038303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放您无尽的愤怒来击败红军。切开机器人，并使用能量提升来获得压倒性的力量。沉浸在受《DOOM》和《Ruiner》等标志性游戏启发的激烈战斗氛围中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/f52b50bab09a8b4968385a6082128d2f.avif?t=1765038303\" width=616 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/08fd5dc14d286ec729038e53b900bd37.poster.avif?t=1765038303\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/08fd5dc14d286ec729038e53b900bd37.webm?t=1765038303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/08fd5dc14d286ec729038e53b900bd37.mp4?t=1765038303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的一举一动都会被跟踪和分析。你做出的每一个决定都已经被预测到了。隐私已经成为一种模糊的记忆。在霓虹灯和后苏联建筑之间，你会看到真相。一切都为系统服务，包括你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/b8fb99dfc6a3af2081f6a5565a79657e.avif?t=1765038303\" width=616 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/a8cd5a9016d0838aabf7c593a4fa3597.poster.avif?t=1765038303\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/a8cd5a9016d0838aabf7c593a4fa3597.webm?t=1765038303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300050/extras/a8cd5a9016d0838aabf7c593a4fa3597.mp4?t=1765038303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越被毁坏的街区和城市的旧区。一睹曾经繁荣的生活。看看系统对那些被认为“不合作”的人做了什么。解放他们。重建叛乱。团结起来对抗红星。</p>",
